div.container
    div.relative
        h1.groupsTitle Manage Groups
        button.btn.btn-primary.addGroupButton(ng-click='openAddGroupModal()') Add Group
        div.alert.alert-danger(ng-show='error' ng-bind='error')
        div.tilePanel
            div(ng-repeat='group in groups | orderBy: name track by $index' ui-sref='home.one')
                div.btn-primary
                    h2 {{group}}
                    p(ng-show='group.indexOf("wef") != -1') This is a long description of this groups and all the information you would ever want to know about it. More... Info... For... longth...
